  Also have |h-2^230 h9|<2^231 so |19 2^(-255)(h-2^230 h9)|<1/4.

  Write y=2^(-1)-19^2 2^(-255)q-19 2^(-255)(h-2^230 h9).
  Then 0<y<1.

  Write r=h-pq.
  Have 0<=r<=p-1=2^255-20.
  Thus 0<=r+19(2^-255)r<r+19(2^-255)2^255<=2^255-1.

  Write x=r+19(2^-255)r+y.
